column2: <START> I love this kind of heart-walking story and this accumulation is the true Olympic spirit thanks to the efforts of all personnel
<START> That's great. That's hard work. Come on
<START> Heat and light, like electricity, can spread. Hope love spreads like a multiplier. All cultures are the same
<START> I like this warm little story to make the world warm now the world is too angry hope all the good people unite to bring peace to the world forever
